---

<section
    class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center relative py-32 bg-[#0f172a] text-[#cbd5e1]"
>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-8">
                <span
                    class="text-[#94a3b8] font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b border-[#94a3b8] pb-2"
                    >El Tiempo Elástico</span
                >
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif italic text-[#f1f5f9]">
                    La Hora Desigual
                </h2>

                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed font-serif text-[#cbd5e1]/90">
                    Hoy vivimos esclavos del "tic-tac" mecánico, donde cada segundo es idéntico al
                    anterior. Pero durante milenios, el tiempo era orgánico.
                </p>

                <div class="space-y-6 mt-8">
                    <div class="bg-[#1e293b] p-6 rounded-sm border-l-2 border-indigo-500/50">
                        <h3 class="text-indigo-200/80 font-bold mb-2">La Hora Romana</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-[#cbd5e1] leading-relaxed">
                            Una "hora" se definía simplemente como 1/12 del tiempo de luz solar.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-xs font-mono text-[#94a3b8]">
                            <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#334155] pb-1">
                                <span>Invierno</span>
                                <span>1 hora = ~45 minutos actuales</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex justify-between pt-1">
                                <span>Verano</span>
                                <span>1 hora = ~75 minutos actuales</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="text-sm text-[#64748b] italic">
                    El tiempo se estiraba y encogía con las estaciones. Nadie llegaba "tarde" porque
                    la tarde misma era flexible.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center relative">
                
                <div class="relative w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" class="w-full h-full drop-shadow-2xl">
                        
                        <circle
                            cx="100"
                            cy="100"
                            r="90"
                            fill="#1e293b"
                            stroke="#334155"
                            stroke-width="2"></circle>

                        
                        <path
                            d="M 30 100 Q 100 30 170 100"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#475569"
                            stroke-width="1"
                            stroke-dasharray="4 4"
                            opacity="0.5"></path>
                        <path
                            d="M 50 100 Q 100 60 150 100"
                            fill="none"
                            stroke="#475569"
                            stroke-width="1"
                            stroke-dasharray="4 4"
                            opacity="0.5"></path>

                        
                        <g stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="1">
                            {
                                Array.from({ length: 13 }).map((_, i) => (
                                    <line
                                        x1="100"
                                        y1="100"
                                        x2="100"
                                        y2="20"
                                        transform={`rotate(${(i - 6) * 15} 100 100)`}
                                        opacity="0.5"
                                    />
                                ))
                            }
                        </g>

                        
                        <g>
                            
                            <path fill="#0f172a" opacity="0.8">
                                <animate
                                    attributeName="d"
                                    values="M 100 100 L 40 100 L 100 100; M 100 100 L 100 20 L 100 100; M 100 100 L 160 100 L 100 100"
                                    dur="10s"
                                    repeatCount="indefinite"
                                    calcMode="spline"
                                    keySplines="0.4 0 0.2 1; 0.4 0 0.2 1"></animate>
                            </path>
                            
                            <line
                                x1="100"
                                y1="100"
                                x2="100"
                                y2="20"
                                stroke="#020617"
                                stroke-width="4"
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                opacity="0.9"
                            >
                                <animateTransform
                                    attributeName="transform"
                                    type="rotate"
                                    values="-80 100 100; 0 100 100; 80 100 100"
                                    dur="10s"
                                    repeatCount="indefinite"
                                    calcMode="spline"
                                    keySplines="0.4 0 0.2 1; 0.4 0 0.2 1"></animateTransform>
                                <animate
                                    attributeName="y2"
                                    values="20; 40; 20"
                                    dur="10s"
                                    repeatCount="indefinite"></animate>
                            </line>
                        </g>

                        
                        <circle
                            cx="100"
                            cy="100"
                            r="6"
                            fill="#e2e8f0"
                            stroke="#475569"
                            stroke-width="2"></circle>

                        
                        <g>
                            <circle cx="100" cy="15" r="8" fill="#fbbf24">
                                <animateTransform
                                    attributeName="transform"
                                    type="rotate"
                                    values="-80 100 100; 0 100 100; 80 100 100"
                                    dur="10s"
                                    repeatCount="indefinite"
                                    calcMode="spline"
                                    keySplines="0.4 0 0.2 1; 0.4 0 0.2 1"></animateTransform>
                            </circle>
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
